            }
        },
        {
            "id": "",
            "content_html": "<p><img src=\"https://pic1.imgdb.cn/item/67d54cb488c538a9b5bec569.png\" alt=\"mermaid\"></p>\n<p>本文是Mermaid基础功能教程，其实主要是因为一鸽鸽太久想不起来Mermaid怎么写，所以给自己建个备忘录（</p>\n<br/><p>访问 <a href=\"https://linium.xin/posts/Mermaid简明指南/index\" target=\"_blank\">https://linium.xin/posts/Mermaid简明指南/index</a> 阅读全文。</p>",
            "url": "https://linium.xin/posts/Mermaid简明指南/index",
            "title": "【Mermaid】简明指南",
            "date_modified": "2025-02-23T00:00:00.000Z",
            "date_published": "2025-05-10T10:34:00.771Z",
            "author": {
